data.description: Step into your dream home with this spacious and inviting 4 bed, 3 bath gem. With a generous 2,796 SF of open floor plan, you'll never feel cramped in this home. As you enter, be prepared to be amazed by the soaring high ceilings, creating a grand and airy ambiance. The two living areas are perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing with family. Imagine cozying up by the wood-burning fireplace on those chilly winter nights. The master bedroom is a true sanctuary, complete with a full bath and a walk-in closet. The true highlight of the master suite is the balcony, where you can sip your morning coffee while enjoying breathtaking views. If you love to cook, you'll fall in love with the kitchen. With ample space for multiple cooks, meal preparations will be a breeze. Plus, its layout ensures that you are always connected to the rest of the main floor, allowing you to chat with loved ones while preparing delicious meals. The breakfast bar and walk-in pantry add that extra touch of convenience. Step outside and be greeted by the tiered entertainment patios, offering both covered and open spaces. The pool and activity center are just a short walk down the street, ensuring endless hours of fun and relaxation. This home is conveniently located near excellent top-rated schools, making it an ideal choice for families. Quick access to Hwy 281 and 1604, plus shopping and dining options are just a stone's throw away.
